	  <concept id="i1082865"
            ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3"
            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">32.412</ph> Contract clause.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d2078e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2092e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contracting officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1049607.dita#i1049607"
                        base="i1049607"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.232-12</xref>, Advance Payments, in solicitations and contracts under which the Government will provide advance payments, except as provided in <xref href="#i1082865"
                        base="i1082865"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.412</xref>(b).</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2092e32" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            If the agency desires to waive the countersignature requirement because of the contractorâ€™s financial strength, good performance record, and favorable experience concerning cost disallowances, the contracting officer shall use the clause with its Alternate I.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2092e41" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            If a cost-reimbursement contract is contemplated, the contracting officer shall use the clause with its AlternateII.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2092e50" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            If the agency considers a more rapid liquidation appropriate, the contracting officer shall use the clause with its AlternateIII.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2092e59" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(e)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            If the agency provides advance payments under the contract at no interest to the prime contractor, the contracting officer shall use the clause with its AlternateIV.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2092e69" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(f)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            If the requirement for a special account is eliminated in accordance with <xref href="FAR-i1082787.dita#i1082787"
                        base="i1082787"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.409-3</xref>(e) or (g), the contracting officer shall insert in the solicitation or contract the clause set forth in Alternate V of <xref href="FAR-i1049607.dita#i1049607"
                        base="i1049607"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.232-12</xref>, Advance Payments, instead of the basic clause.</p>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
		    </conbody>
